description:
&lt;p&gt;Our vision is to be a consistently high performing and financially sustainable Trust by April 2021. By joining us now, you can play a role in making this vision a reality. This is an excellent opportunity to join our Trust Board and be part of an exciting new chapter of our Trust’s future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the Director of Operational Estates , you will be required to give assurance to the Trust Executive and Trust Board that all technical matters relating building services in respect of hard FM (and soft FM), with an emphasis on all mechanical and electrical services; for all areas within the retained estate are compliant, appropriate and proportionate. This includes advice received from; technical advisors; consultants: PFI partners: service contract and contracted services partners; construction contractors, etc. You will also be responsible for all Trust and Community Estate including Freehold and Leasehold properties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, I am looking for an astute, driven, flexible and determined individual who can meet the challenge, and who will be committed to driving forward our future plans. I am also looking for someone who has expertise in complex business case development for investment in the public sector, with strong stakeholder engagement skills, demonstrating the ability to manage stakeholder expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return, you could be part of an upward journey, in which there is both permission and support to be innovative, in order to ensure the Trust overcomes its present and future challenges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJim LusbyJob titleDirector of Strategy and IntegrationEmail addressjim.lusby@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
